## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] If work involves Google Drive files, share/open them before starting — Gemini reads linked files natively
- [ ] Use Gemini Advanced or API for full tool access
- [ ] For large document sets: upload directly or link from Drive rather than pasting
- [ ] Enable Google Search if real-time data is needed
- [ ] For Workspace automation: confirm Gemini has access to the relevant Google apps
